emuInput.TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Mr. and Mrs. Walter Wells, posed in their home on Iowa Street for fiftieth wedding anniversary party
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 21, 1956, pg. A14, reads: "50 Years of Wedded Bliss - Golden Year - Mr. and Mrs. Walter Wells of Iowa Street celebrated their fiftieth wedding anniversary Jan. 15 quietly with their family about them. They have three children, Mrs. Narvella Green, Eugenia and Fred wells, and four grandchildren. - Harris Photo."
